        "description": "All 4 endpoints for Capital Meter / Capital Power Systems prepaid meter API.\nGenerated by Antigravity Integration Engine following skills.md Step 3.\n\nGrid Server: https://smartprepaidmeters.com\nDG Server: http://dg.smartprepaidmeters.com\nSociety: Spectrum Metro Mall (Comm ID: 52060)",
